data.meta_description: February 20: Eleanor of Aragon Queen of Castile was a daughter of King Peter IV of Aragon and his wife Eleanor of Sicily. She was a member of the House of Aragon and Queen of Castile by her marriage. She was born in El Puig Spain on this day in 1358.  #thisday #thisdayinhistory #february #febrero #history #hispanichistory #hispanicheritage #genealogy #shhar #shharorganization #somosprimos #wearecousins #hispanicgenealogy #newspain #nuevaespana #newworld  #castile #castilla #aragon #aragona #elea
